Start a Gociety plan whenever you’re heading outdoors, and get some awesome people to join you. Post last-minute or a week before. Gociety is all about creating spontaneous, one-time get togethers. You have the chance to accept or deny members into your Gociety plan, ensuring you get outside with the best people for any adventure.

Trip reports are trip reports from adventures you’ve been on. Gociety is all about spontaneity and discovery, and posting a Trip report is the best way to share your experiences with the Gociety community, and be inspired by the places other people have gone. Think of it as a visual journal for your outdoor life.
For best results use horizontal photos. Optimal banner size is 720 x 250 px and less than 10MB. You can add up to 5 images.
